  "nodes": [
    {
      "type": "adr-preamble",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003eAdopted after the spike in sprint 12.\u003c/p\u003e\n",
      "raw": true
    },
    {
      "type": "adr-context",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003eWe need a relational database. This revisits \u003ca href=\"decisions/0003-use-sqlite.adr/\"\u003e003\u003c/a\u003e\nand its \u003ca href=\"decisions/0003-use-sqlite.adr/#decision\"\u003edecision\u003c/a\u003e. Background reading:\n\u003ca href=\"https://example.com/notes.adr.md\"\u003ehttps://example.com/notes.adr.md\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n",
      "raw": true
    },
    {
      "type": "adr-decision",
      "content": "\u003cp\u003eWe will use \u003cstrong\u003ePostgreSQL\u003c/strong\u003e for all persistent storage.\u003c/p\u003e\n",
      "raw": true
    },
    {
      "type": "adr-consequences",
      "content": "\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eStrong ecosystem\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eOperational overhead\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n",
      "raw": true
    },
    {
      "type": "adr-options-considered",
      "content": "\u003ctable\u003e\n\u003cthead\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eOption\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003cth\u003eVerdict\u003c/th\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/thead\u003e\n\u003ctbody\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003eSQLite\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003etoo small\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003ctr\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003ePostgreSQL\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003ctd\u003echosen\u003c/td\u003e\n\u003c/tr\u003e\n\u003c/tbody\u003e\n\u003c/table\u003e\n",
